  s01: <
    handle: "custom-boof/01"
    type: "custom-boof"
    excerpt: "Boof stood at the edge of the clearing, the last echoes of their awakening still resonating within. Before them, a new path opened, stretching out into the unknown. It was not a maze, nor a game—it was something else,..."
