    handle: "custom-path/02"
    type: "custom-path"
    excerpt: "The path was quiet, unassuming, but full of promise. Boof knew that the journey had changed—no longer about solving puzzles or chasing the Fool. This was about walking forward, with no end in sight, but with a newfoun..."
