  s03: <
    handle: "custom-fool/03"
    type: "custom-fool"
    excerpt: "\"You’ve come far, Boof,\" the Fool’s voice echoed softly. \"But the path ahead is yours to choose. It’s no longer about games, but about what you make of it.\""
